## Scan logic:

- [x] Scan for filename, mtime and length
- [ ] Add to db
- [ ] Check info with db. If size change, backup file.
  - [ ] If no mtime change, continue.
  - [ ] If mtime change, check hash
    - [ ] If hash changed, backup file.
    - [ ] If no change, update mtime

